{"tid":473833,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"city先有資格入圍做新三大","createTime":"2017-11-19T14:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T15:40:33.000Z","uid":49974,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f44917521325bca9d9466153ea04778a575b3af","tid":473833,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:30:35.000Z","msg":"近年QS排名節節上升已經係一個好好嘅例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aafad998d7cf269388e41f2258d684639025f4b","tid":473833,"uid":140580,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:45:46.000Z","msg":"你煩唔煩"},{"pid":"401bae2ca7797d415bd9081b2be7693b5f872625","tid":473833,"uid":132968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">城大涉「篤數」谷排名 科大校長都搲頭諗唔明</span><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》揭發城大疑在學生人數「報細數」，藉以誇大師生比例力谷國際機構QS的大學排名；城大事後向師生發電郵，斥報道不正確，對此強烈不滿，但未解釋報予QS學生人數與教資會所列學生人數差距達三成的原因。科大校長陳繁昌今稱未有在大學校會討論此事，也不知城大實際情況，僅稱教資會與QS的人數呈報可能不同，但不會差太遠，「譬如差三、四十巴仙，嘩你真係要搲吓頭喇，點解呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171113/57454109\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57454109&d=kYqbks8eUmnrBUD5tZVkzgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b3a9a6e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57454109&h=84ee42b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171113/57454109</a>"}]}